eneous\nradio properties of NLSy1s with their strict optical line criteria, and\nnear-term prospects for the discovery of larger numbers of radio-loud NLSy1s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2018 16:12:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-15"}
