06989B and HD 205403B, measured by KELT\nand STEREO photometry, are $17-20\\%$ higher than those predicted by theory. A\nbrief comparison of the results of the current work is made with the M dwarfs\nalready studied in literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 May 2018 15:18:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-11"}
